    <!--  First About Content Start  -->
    <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-12" data-scroll-reveal="enter left move 30px over 0.6s after 0.4s">
                    <img src="~/resources/images/about-left-image.png" class="rounded img-fluid d-block mx-auto" alt="First About Image">
                </div>
                <div class="right-text col-lg-5 col-md-12 col-sm-12 mobile-top-fix">
                    <div class="left-heading">
                        <h1><b>Making every student unstoppable</b></h1>
                    </div>
                    <br>
                    <div class="left-text">
                        <p>
                            At Flashcard, we believe that anyone can learn anything. All it takes is a tenacious spirit, the right guidance and the tools to see it through.
                            We know that students are under more pressure than ever. It can leave them feeling overwhelmed, produce anxiety and make it all too easy to burn out.
                            It’s our job to give every student the tools and confidence to succeed, no matter their motivation or what they’re striving to achieve.
                        </p>
                        <br><br>
                        <a href="#about2" class="main-button">Read our impact report</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!--  First About Content End  -->


    <!-- Abour Stats Start -->
    <div style="align-content: center;" data-scroll-reveal="enter left move 30px over 0.6s after 0.4s">
